———————————————————————







20) We Can get the Emails which are Following the below mentioned Rules

SELECT * FROM users WHERE email REGEXP '^[a-z0-9._]+@[a-z0-9_]+\.[a-z]{2,}';


Rules for Valid Email are


For Name Valid is [a-z, 0-9, ., _]

For Domain Valid is [a-z, 0-9]

For Top Level Domain Valid is [a-z 2 or More Characters]


name - sumit
domain - "trendytech" "gmail"
top level domain - ".in" ".com"



- Some Demo Emails

sumit@trendytech.in
sumit_hyd@gmail.com
trendytech.sumit@gmail.com


name@domain.topleveldomain




